<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Basecamp - Project Management & Team Communication Software</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'styles', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Kalam&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div data-controller="home">
        <header class="header">
            <%= render 'shared/logo' %>
            
            <nav class="nav-links" data-home-target="navLinks">
                <%= render 'shared/navigation' %>
            </nav>
            
            <div class="hamburger-menu" 
                 data-home-target="hamburger"
                 data-action="click->home#toggleMenu">
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="main-content">
            <div class="content-left">
                <h1>Wrestling with projects?<br>It doesn't have to be this hard.</h1>
                <p class="questions">Stuff scattered? Falling behind?<br>Even simple things feel like a grind?</p>
                <p class="tagline">Your projects need Basecamp.</p>
                <p class="description">Basecamp frees you up. It's for makers, not micromanagers. For shipping, not slipping. It's all about making progress.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content-right">
                <%= render 'shared/preview_card' %>
            </div>
        </main>

        <%= render 'shared/testimonials' %>
        <%= render 'shared/cta_section' %>
        <%= render 'shared/bento_grid' %>
        <%= render 'shared/faq_section' %>
        <%= render 'shared/footer' %>
    </div>

    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
</body>
</html>